    <div class="container clearfix">
        <h2>Example 1: Without Clear</h2>
        <div class="floated-box float-left">Float Left</div>
        <p>This paragraph will wrap around the floated box. The floated box is taken out of the normal document flow, allowing subsequent content to flow beside it. This is normal float behavior.</p>
        <p>More content here that continues to wrap around the floated element.</p>
